Package: securetrace
Title: Observability and Tracing for R LLM Agent Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ian", "Flores Siaca", , "iflores.siaca@hey.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Structured traces with spans, token and cost accounting,
    latency monitoring, and JSONL export for R-based LLM agent workflows.
    Follows OpenTelemetry-inspired patterns adapted for R AI applications.
